@node Prerequisites
@section Prerequisites

Before using this package, you must:

@enumerate
@item
Install @uref{https://mullvad.net/, Mullvad VPN} on your system.
@item
Log in via the terminal: @samp{mullvad account login YOUR_ACCOUNT_NUMBER}. You can find your account number under ``Settings'' > ``Account'' in the Mullvad graphical interface.
@item
Ensure the @samp{mullvad} command-line tool is on your @code{exec-path}. The package attempts to locate it automatically when loaded; if it cannot be found, you must set @code{mullvad-executable} manually (@ref{Executable path}).
@end enumerate

@node Installation
@section Installation

@menu
* Manual::
* With use-package::
@end menu

@node Manual
@subsection Manual

Clone the repository and add it to your @code{load-path}:

@lisp
(add-to-list 'load-path "/path/to/mullvad")
(require 'mullvad)
@end lisp

@node With use-package
@subsection With use-package

@lisp
;; with vc (Emacs 30+)
(use-package mullvad
  :vc (:url "https://github.com/benthamite/mullvad"))

;; with elpaca
(use-package mullvad
  :ensure (:host github :repo "benthamite/mullvad"))

;; with straight
(use-package mullvad
  :straight (:host github :repo "benthamite/mullvad"))

;; with quelpa
(use-package mullvad
  :quelpa (mullvad :fetcher github :repo "benthamite/mullvad"))
@end lisp

